name: Cohegeen
description: Rush is a worker at one of the factories in Kuala Lumpur. One day, he found a big hole while digging the ground. He decided to go near the hole. Suddenly, he slipped and fell into the hole. The environment was so different. It was full of neon light. So he decided to find his way back. He runs to find his way back to his real world. But there are a lot of obstacles that he has to go through. Will Rush find his way back safely?
